Package com.mazeco.models

Class MazeModel

java.lang.Object
com.mazeco.models.MazeModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class MazeModel extends Object implements Serializable
Represents the data and configuration of a maze to be stored in MazeRecord.
